\id 3JN  
\h 3 Yohanes 
\toc1 Surat ni YOHANES Men Koporotoluna 
\toc2 3 Yohanes 
\toc3 3Yoh. 
\mt2 Surat ni 
\mt1 YOHANES 
\mt2 Men Koporotoluna 
\c 1  
\s1 Tabea' 
\sr 1-4 
\p  
\v 1 Yaku' penatua. 
\p Bona i Gayus, men kolingu'ku men parasaya na pisiso' men kana'.\x * \xo 1:1 \xt Tun. 19:29; Rm. 16:23; 1Kor. 1:14 \x* 
\p  
\v 2 Utusku men kolingu'ku! Yaku' sambayangkon kada' i koo sulano sian nongko'upa ka' malesi' na giigii' tutuo'om, koi men yaku' inti'i santuo'om uga' sian nongko'upa.  
\v 3 Yaku' nobeles tuu' gause isian toropii utus men sa'angu' kaparasaya'an taka nambantilkon na ingku' se' i koo malolo' na pisiso' men kana', ka' tumuo' mongololo' pisiso' men kana' iya'a.  
\v 4 Sianta upa sambana men kobelesku saliwakon nongorongor lele se' anakku tumuo' mongololo' pisiso' men kana'. 
\s1 Yohanes nuntunde' i Gayus 
\sr 5-8 
\p  
\v 5 Utusku men kolingu'ku! Koo malolo' tuu' mangalawei utus sa'angu' kaparasaya'an maupo mianna sianpo koo inti'i.  
\v 6 Raaya'a nuntundunkonmo na jama'at se' i koo molingu'kon tuu' i raaya'a. Pore uga' kalu i koo mantarai upa men bo kokosidana i raaya'a na salan gause wawau men koiya'a daa kikira'na Alaata'ala.  
\v 7 Supu-supuana mingilimang palimangonna i Kristus, raaya'a namarereimo laiganna see sian nangalabot upa-upa na mian men sian minginti'i Alaata'ala.  
\v 8 Mbaka' i kita tio mangalawei simbaya'ta men koiya'a, kada' i kita uga' tonsoop munsunsungkon i raaya'a mengelelekon pisiso' men kana'. 
\s1 Diotrepes tii Demetrius 
\sr 9-12 
\p  
\v 9 Yaku' nuntulismo surat titiu' bona jama'at, kasee i Diotrefes men mingkira' tongaan se' ia bo pinginti'i sian mansangadai i kai.  
\v 10 Mbaka' kalu i yaku' taka, pa'ase'onku kada' pakanasai a upa men limangonna, gause ia nengeneengkon wurung men ba'idek na ko'omai. Wawauna men koiya'a sianpo kinodaana. Ia taasi' tongko' kundakon utus sa'angu' kaparasaya'an men taka, kasee ia uga' mongkokundakon mianna jama'at men nangalaboti mian men tumaka iya'a. Ia nanggau'kon mian men nangalaboti pataka i raaya'a notonguar na jama'at. 
\p  
\v 11 Utusku men kolingu'ku! Alia mongololo' men ba'idek, kasee lolo' a men pore. Mian men mingilimang pore, ia ringkat na Alaata'ala, kasee mian men mingilimang ba'idek, ia sianpo ninginti'i Alaata'ala. 
\p  
\v 12 Giigii' mian mompotuutuu' wawau men pore ni Demetrius. Ka' uga' limangna men kana' iya'a mompotuutuu' i ia. Kai uga' mompotuutuu' wawauna men pore. Ka' koo inti'i se' men taemai kani'i tuutuu'. 
\s1 Taa' kakabusanna 
\sr 13-15 
\p  
\v 13 Biai' tuu' a men bo bantilkononku na ko'oom, kasee surionku sian pore kalu tongko' na surat.  
\v 14 Ooskononku sulano i yaku' dongan poorurumpak tii koo kada' i kita sida poowewer. 
\p  
\v 15 Sulano koratongan surioon na tutuo'om. Samba-sambaam men isian tii yaku' moki tundunkon salamna bo ko'oom. Yaku' moki tundunkon salamku na giigii' samba-sambaam sa'angu'-sa'angu'.